            "a5": "In student details, click \"Send current status\". This generates a pre-filled WhatsApp message with balance and lesson info.",
            "q6": "How to change app color?",
            "a6": "Go to \"Profile\" tab. Select a color in \"Theme Color\" and press \"Save\".",
            "q7": "How to backup data?",
            "a7": "In \"Profile\" > \"Data and Backup\", press \"Backup (Export)\". Save the file. Use \"Restore\" to load it back."
